<br>
Think of it this way.  An Enchanter in any guild with a charmed mob could easily out dmg two groups.  (Groups who aren't in my guild or in a rival guild of equal power on my server... But could probably outdmg one of our 6 man groups.)  The dps on these things is truely amazing.<br>
<br>
